title: Unable to install November patch
content:
I'm on build QD1A.190821.011.C4. When I go to sideload the new image ( 10.0.0 (QD1A.190821.014, Nov 2019) )  from Google I get this error:

>package is older than the current build, expected a build newer than timestapmp 1570131307 but package has timestmp 1569028385 and downgrade not allowed.

Yet I am still showing on the October security patch. No OTA available when checking from my phone.
